column5: Hi Bobwas up to Ernies and fished out at Stephenson pulled the boat out with the quads told Kenny that I had talked to you on the net he was surprised that your were on the net.Kenny seems to be taking a bigger part in the work there.Mostly came up to try out the new camper. Thanks for the info. concerning the beautiful area up there.len in michigan
Have ya been up to earnies lately????
